Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: rcforge
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash (>= 4.0)
Description: Universal shell configuration system
 rcForge is a flexible, modular configuration system for Bash and Zsh shells
 that provides a single framework for managing shell environments across
 multiple machines. It features:
 .
 * Cross-shell compatibility with Bash and Zsh
 * Machine-specific configurations using hostname detection
 * Deterministic loading order with explicit sequence numbers
 * Conflict detection to identify and resolve loading conflicts
 * Integrated include system for modular function organization
 * Visual diagrams of configuration loading order
 .
 Currently in version 0.2.0 (pre-release)
